<p> οιὐμύρ<supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied>
<lb/>
          Ἐγω Ἡσύχις ἐνθάδε κῖμε σὺν τῆ ἐμῇ συνβίῳ<lb/>
					πᾶς τολμῶν ἀνῦξε ἐφ’ <supplied reason="lost">ἡ</supplied>μᾶς μὴ ἔχῃ μέρος εἰς τὸν<lb/>
<supplied reason="lost">Βίον</supplied> ἀόνιο<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied>. </p>
</div>
<div ana="#b4" corresp="#beth0129.transcription" type="translation" xml:id="beth0129.translation">
<p>I, <persName ref="persons.xml#beth0129p01" xml:lang="grc ">Hesychios</persName>, <rs ana="interpretations.xml#lie" type="formula">lie here </rs> with my <rs ana="interpretations.xml#wife" type="family">wife</rs>. <rs type="formula">May anyone who dares to open (the
						grave) above us not have a portion in the eternal life</rs>.</p>
</div>
</body>
